This is bad because after 19. e3 black can't stop all the threats, which includes 20. Bxc4 and Qe5+.  Black can't defend with 19. ... Qe7 or Qf6  because of a pending Nxd5.  Castling kingside is suicidal because of Qg3+ and Qh3.  If instead 19. ... Rg8 (or something dumb like Kd7) then 21. O-O-O and with Nxd5 coming, black 's position is in shambles.  So computer analysis prefers 18. ... Qb8 giving up material.
